INSERT INTO `questions` (`id`,`skill_id`,`exam_id`,`subject_id`,`position`,`label`,`content`) VALUES (21163,239,7,30,142,'137','<img src=\"https://img.enem.appprova.com.br/questions/images/21163/original/enem_2015_15.png\" /><p>A figura representa a vista superior de uma bola de futebol&nbsp;americano, cuja forma &eacute; um elipsoide obtido pela rota&ccedil;&atilde;o de uma elipse em torno do eixo das abscissas. Os valores a e b s&atilde;o, respectivamente, a metade do seu comprimento horizontal e a metade do seu comprimento vertical. Para essa bola, a diferen&ccedil;a entre os comprimentos horizontal e vertical &eacute; igual &agrave; metade do comprimento vertical.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Considere que o volume aproximado dessa bola &eacute; dado por $V = 4ab^2$ .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>O volume dessa bola, em fun&ccedil;&atilde;o apenas de b, &eacute; dado por</p>\r\n');
INSERT INTO `questions` (`id`,`skill_id`,`exam_id`,`subject_id`,`position`,`label`,`content`) VALUES (21166,275,7,25,91,'91I','<p><strong>NOTICE OF BAGGAGE INSPECTION</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>To protect you and your fellow passengers, the Transportation Security Administration (TSA) is required by law to inspect all checked baggage.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As part of this process, some bags are opened and physically inspected. Your bag was among those selected for physical inspection.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>During the inspection, your bag and its contents may have been searched for prohibited items. At the completion of the inspection, the contents were returned to your bag.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If the TSA security officer was unable to open your bag for inspection because it was locked, the officer may have been forced to break the locks on your bag. TSA sincerely regrets having to do this, however TSA is not liable for damage to your locks resulting from this necessary security precaution.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For packing tips and suggestions on how to secure your baggage during your next trip, please visit:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>www.tsa.gov</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Smart Security Saves Time</p>\r\n\r\n<p><sub>Transportation Security Administration. Dispon&iacute;vel em: www.tsa.gov. Acesso em: 13 jan. 2010 (adaptado).</sub></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As institui&ccedil;&otilde;es p&uacute;blicas fazem uso de avisos como instrumento de comunica&ccedil;&atilde;o com o cidad&atilde;o. Esse aviso, voltado a passageiros, tem o objetivo de</p>\r\n');
INSERT INTO `questions` (`id`,`skill_id`,`exam_id`,`subject_id`,`position`,`label`,`content`) VALUES (21169,260,7,30,143,'138','<img src=\"https://img.enem.appprova.com.br/questions/images/21169/original/enem_2015_16.png\" /><p>Ap&oacute;s realizar uma pesquisa de mercado, uma operadora de telefonia celular ofereceu aos clientes que utilizavam at&eacute; 500 liga&ccedil;&otilde;es ao m&ecirc;s o seguinte plano mensal: um valor fixo de&nbsp;R\\$ 12,00 para os clientes que&nbsp;fazem at&eacute; 100 liga&ccedil;&otilde;es ao m&ecirc;s. Caso o cliente fa&ccedil;a mais de 100 liga&ccedil;&otilde;es, ser&aacute; cobrado um valor adicional de R\\$ 0,10 por liga&ccedil;&atilde;o, a partir da 101&ordf; at&eacute; a 300&ordf;; e caso realize entre 300 e 500 liga&ccedil;&otilde;es, ser&aacute; cobrado um valor fixo mensal de R\\$ 32,00.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Com base nos elementos apresentados, o gr&aacute;fico que&nbsp;melhor representa a rela&ccedil;&atilde;o entre o valor mensal pago nesse plano e o n&uacute;mero de liga&ccedil;&otilde;es feitas &eacute;:&nbsp;</p>\r\n');
